model_summary: A simple utility model combining fairness and self-interest. The model uses two learnable parameters: a fairness parameter (β) constrained to [0,1] and a self-interest parameter (γ) constrained to [0,1]. The utility is calculated as a function of the difference between the proposed shares and the participant's token contribution.
